reviewText:
This Is A Rare Video . i Don't Think That It Was ever Sold In The US. I Bought This Video Because
It Has An Early Version Of The Very Popular Worship Song "Shout To The Lord" On It. This Song Was
Written By Darlene Zschech, And Is Sung By Her On This Video. Shout To The Lord Is Sung By An
Estimated 25-30 Million Churchgoers Every Week. As You Watch This Video, You Will see The Joy Of
The Lord On The Faces Of The People !
